  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/0fe61181ab8255fbd9df4abeb99223fb.avif?t=1734045135\" width=600 height=145 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/cedf5237b5af8117c4fc6a44cc7bdefa.avif?t=1734045135\" width=500 height=145 /></span><br><br>You travel to a cabin to try and find your sister who has been missing for a few days. Once arriving in the woods you get trapped and are forced to stay at the cabin while you look for her. The wildlife around the cabin seems a little bit too supernatural for your liking. Spend the days looking for your sister and collecting resources. Spend the night struggling to hide and survive against the creatures of the night.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/d27f92de3f3160562b066cf62fc05ac0.poster.avif?t=1734045135\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/d27f92de3f3160562b066cf62fc05ac0.webm?t=1734045135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/d27f92de3f3160562b066cf62fc05ac0.mp4?t=1734045135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/07c889609d51026b375a9416e8aa5c0c.avif?t=1734045135\" width=500 height=145 /></span><br><br>• Look for your sister<br>• Explore the forest<br>• Collect Resources for the night<br>• Keep an eye out for creatures<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/18310e4c115d96ebb56ac2a9689c4f32.poster.avif?t=1734045135\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/18310e4c115d96ebb56ac2a9689c4f32.webm?t=1734045135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/18310e4c115d96ebb56ac2a9689c4f32.mp4?t=1734045135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/92398d8a11e30977828313d2bfe1719e.avif?t=1734045135\" width=500 height=145 /></span><br>• Peer out the cabin to keep an eye on the creatures<br>• Figure out how to survive the night<br>• Keep your fire stoked<br>• Keep the door locked<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/7cb2048d1d8c75952ea39b1025ed573d.poster.avif?t=1734045135\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/7cb2048d1d8c75952ea39b1025ed573d.webm?t=1734045135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/7cb2048d1d8c75952ea39b1025ed573d.mp4?t=1734045135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957330/extras/0813bdce0935b2226eeec0a02670c292.avif?t=1734045135\" width=500 height=145 /></span><br>Hey there, I'm Raven Clancey, a solo game dev with a real passion for stirring up emotions in players. I'm all about creating games that pull you in and make you feel something real, whether it's heart-pounding excitement or a wave of nostalgia. I pour my heart and soul into every pixel, line of code, and killer soundtrack to create experiences that stick with you long after you've stopped playing. In my games, you're not just playing—you're living through a rollercoaster of emotions, all carefully crafted by yours truly.",
